Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:17.72,White,,0,0,0,,No pot... no pot ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:25.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(veu Shinichi) "Uns ulls plorosos arriben al cor."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.20,0:00:27.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Les llàgrimes indiquen l'inici d'una tragèdia."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.36,0:00:29.36,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Un incident inesperat, creix el misteri...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:31.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,i apareix una segona sala tancada."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.68,0:00:33.68,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"La veritat sempre s'acaba sabent."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:36.56,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Sembla un nen, però té el cervell d'un adult i és el detectiu Conan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.56,0:00:40.92,Songs,,0,0,0,,Ano toki mita sora, furasshu bakku shita futo shita.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.48,0:00:45.00,Songs,,0,0,0,,Futoshita shunkan anata wo kanjita.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:49.08,Songs,,0,0,0,,Kokoro no shattaa orikaketa no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.44,0:00:52.48,Songs,,0,0,0,,yuuhi ni ukanda anata no kao.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.96,0:01:00.32,Songs,,0,0,0,,Why, why, why, wakatteru no ni ienakatta.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.72,0:01:06.76,Songs,,0,0,0,,Lie, lie, soba ni ite hoshii I want your love.
