Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.72,0:01:15.44,Songs,,0,0,0,,Tear drops sou desho naite irun janai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.44,0:01:19.96,Songs,,0,0,0,,Tear drops sou desho zutto wasurenai ai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:23.88,Songs,,0,0,0,,Tear drops, tear drops, kono nazo toite tear drops.
